ğŸ“Œ Same design language, different intent.

8ï¸âƒ£ FINANCIAL UX & SECURITY RULES (CRITICAL)

Every money action requires:

Confirmation

PIN or biometric

Sensitive info:

Hidden by default

Revealed only on user action

Show warnings in calm language

Never auto-spend user money

